Mero, one of the largest floor manufacturers in the UE, offers innovative solutions for raised access floors. Panel surfaces applied with textile, parquet, stone, ceramic, elastic or hard finishes can be fitted in different environments: industrial, office, and laboratories. Mero panels made of fibre-reinforced mineral non-combustible, wooden reinforced with steel sheets, or construction type of the materials, allow for high load bearing, humidity conditions, and protection against corrosion with conductive coating.